data.description: Stunning turnkey pool home spanning over 3,000 sq. ft. featuring 4 bedrooms with the possibility of 3 additional optional bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a 3-car garage, and RV parking! This well-maintained property boasts beautiful landscaping, fresh interior and exterior paint, gleaming hardwood flooring, and even comes with FREE Solar. There are numerous upgrades that enhance the home, including a water softener system throughout. As you step inside, you'll find a formal dining area to the right and a formal living room (currently being used as a home gym studio) to the left. Beyond the stairs is the family room with expansive windows offering picturesque views of the backyard oasis. The recently renovated kitchen, perfect for entertaining, is equipped with brand-new quartz countertops, an elegant tile backsplash, white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious pantry. It also features a trendy butcher block countertop with a built-in wine fridge (this can also be an additional bedroom and is currently being used as a home theater). Before entering the garage, there is an additional room that is currently being used as a spa room but can easily be repurposed as a home office, a small business owner's space, an additional walk-in linen closet, or whatever your heart desires. Step out into the backyard through beautiful double French doors that open to your private paradise. You'll find a saltwater pool, a covered patio, a spacious built-in BBQ area, and a beautifully turfed side yard, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. This home is conveniently located just off the I-215, providing quick access to shops, restaurants, the hospital, and Temecula Wine Country. Best of all, there's no HOA to worry about!
